<div class="css-bz2tic css-dpvz6t"><div class="css-628mvu css-roiesn css-qzkf75"></div><p class="css-mshi22 css-v4058c css-roiesn css-14etce textContents"><span class="css-hu9wtw css-a49u1q">Maximize Your Space</span><span class="css-hu9wtw css-b54yok"> with Attached Garage Conversions and ADUs</span></p><div class="css-v511zc css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-ki8et9 textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3vgump">An Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU) is a self-contained living space built on the same lot as your primary home. Whether attached, detached, or integrated into your existing house, each option offers unique advantages depending on your property, budget, and long-term goals.</p></div><div class="css-bz2tic css-dqbxpu"><div class="css-pj6ukt css-roiesn css-atgcpy"></div><div class="css-hry8ah css-roiesn css-rqi8kd"></div><div class="css-hrvocd css-roiesn css-rqi8kd"></div><div class="css-hrfmmt css-roiesn css-rqi8kd"></div><div class="css-dvs7qv css-roiesn css-rqi8kd"></div><div class="css-dvut5i css-roiesn css-rqi8kd"></div><div class="css-dwatej css-roiesn css-rqi8kd"></div><p class="css-tzn6qh css-cvyp7t css-bx4uyo css-6fjkjm textContents">Add a private living space above your garage while preserving your yard and parking. A smart solution for maximizing limited lot space.</p><p class="css-tzn6qh css-cvw59p css-bx4uyo css-6fjkjm textContents">A detached ADU is a standalone home with its own entrance, kitchen, bathroom, and living space. It offers maximum privacy and excellent rental income potential.</p><div class="css-cwerfg css-roiesn css-pf7n4 css-6fjkjm textContents"><p class="css-8jchzs css-3yrm6v">A JADU transforms part of your existing home into a self-contained space with its own entrance and kitchenette. It benefits from California's simplified permitting process.</p><p class="css-8zr56v css-npmnc8">​</p></div><p class="css-tzn6qh css-pka6yd css-bx4uyo css-6fjkjm textContents">An attached ADU shares a wall with the main house while maintaining a private entrance and full living amenities. It offers a cost-effective way to expand your property.</p><div class="css-pkcqtw css-roiesn css-pf7n4 css-6fjkjm textContents"><p class="css-8jchzs css-drr5ym">Convert your existing garage into a fully permitted ADU. Since the structure already exists, projects are typically faster and more affordable.</p><p class="css-8jchzs css-6m1nlr">​</p><p class="css-8jchzs css-6m1nlr">​</p><p class="css-8zr56v css-6m1nlr">​</p></div><div class="css-pkst44 css-roiesn css-pf7n4 css-6fjkjm textContents"><p class="css-8jchzs css-drr5ym">A two-story ADU maximizes living space by building vertically, making it ideal for smaller lots while preserving valuable outdoor areas.</p><p class="css-8jchzs css-6m1nlr">​</p><p class="css-8zr56v css-6m1nlr">​</p></div><div class="css-c6gfuu css-tflapp css-8zrmd9 css-xbwo2m textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3xo105">A fully independent unit built in your backyard.</p></div><div class="css-e2mxfm css-tflapp css-8zrmd9 css-xbwo2m textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3xo105">Build up, not out — and keep your parking.</p></div><div class="css-ne2xjn css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-aeu6m0 textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-4cih0w">Homeowners with a detached garage who want to maximize their property's potential.</p></div><div class="css-mruzhe css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-fvillh textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3yrm6v">Best for:</p></div><div class="css-lhwfyv css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-aeu6m0 textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-4cih0w">Homeowners with available backyard space who want maximum rental income or a fully private family suite.</p></div><div class="css-mrxjfi css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-fvillh textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3yrm6v">Best for:</p></div><div class="css-qaxnt6 css-tflapp css-8zrmd9 css-xbwo2m textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3xo105">Convert existing space into a functional living unit.</p></div><div class="css-zf3ss0 css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-aeu6m0 textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-4cih0w">Homeowners who want an affordable ADU using existing interior space.</p></div><div class="css-mrei79 css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-fvillh textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3yrm6v">Best for:</p></div><div class="css-isagh0 css-roiesn"><div class="css-o7b50b css-trglf0"><img alt="" class="css-trglf0 css-qw3zwa" loading="lazy" sizes="auto,1068.6349170692197px" src="/images/Attached ADU.png" style="object-fit: contain !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; position: relative !important; top: 0 !important; left: 0 !important; max-width: none !important;"/></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="css-fe0ykj css-ggwoeh css-5eam1e"></div></div><div class="css-rdcjzi css-7g786b css-8zrmd9 css-tv82io textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3hpzso">Attached ADU</p></div><div class="css-1tz7d0 css-tflapp css-8zrmd9 css-xbwo2m textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3xo105">More space, connected to your home.</p></div><div class="css-sqgevl css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-aeu6m0 textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-4cih0w">Homeowners who want to add living space or rental income without using backyard square footage.</p></div><div class="css-kaizum css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-fvillh textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3yrm6v">Best for:</p></div><div class="css-2lywx css-tflapp css-8zrmd9 css-xbwo2m textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3xo105">Your most cost-effective path to rental income.</p></div><div class="css-gjp8cy css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-aeu6m0 textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-4cih0w">Homeowners with an unused garage who want the quickest and most cost-effective ADU option.</p></div><div class="css-kazf1u css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-fvillh textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3yrm6v">Best for:</p></div><div class="css-4jygia css-roiesn"><div class="css-o7b50b css-trglf0"><img alt="" class="css-trglf0 css-z3as1s" loading="lazy" sizes="auto,1068.6349170692197px" src="/images/Detached ADU.png" style="object-fit: contain !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; position: relative !important; top: 0 !important; left: 0 !important; max-width: none !important;"/></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="css-fe0ykj css-ggwoeh css-5eam1e"></div></div><div class="css-jizx1m css-7g786b css-8zrmd9 css-tv82io textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3hpzso">Detached ADU</p></div><div class="css-5ns3tt css-roiesn"><div class="css-o7b50b css-trglf0"><img alt="" class="css-trglf0 css-9edryz" loading="lazy" sizes="auto,263.64134825245566px" src="/images/Above-Garage ADU.png" style="object-fit: contain !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; position: relative !important; top: 0 !important; left: 0 !important; max-width: none !important;"/></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="css-fe0ykj css-ggwoeh css-5eam1e"></div></div><div class="css-ooeuwn css-7g786b css-8zrmd9 css-tv82io textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3hpzso">Above-Garage ADU</p></div><div class="css-cai0lc css-tflapp css-8zrmd9 css-xbwo2m textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3xo105">Double the space without expanding your footprint.</p></div><div class="css-emclnc css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-aeu6m0 textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-4cih0w">Homeowners who need more square footage without sacrificing backyard space.</p></div><div class="css-kb212v css-lla91 css-8zrmd9 css-fvillh textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3yrm6v">Best for:</p></div><div class="css-hoha6l css-roiesn"><div class="css-o7b50b css-trglf0"><img alt="" class="css-trglf0 css-y9pif0" loading="lazy" sizes="auto,302.61081812119073px" src="/images/Garage Conversion.png" style="object-fit: contain !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; position: relative !important; top: 0 !important; left: 0 !important; max-width: none !important;"/></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="css-fe0ykj css-ggwoeh css-5eam1e"></div></div><div class="css-e3yc09 css-7g786b css-8zrmd9 css-tv82io textContents"><p class="css-8zr56v css-3hpzso">Garage Con